Researcher --> UC13
Researcher --> UC14
Researcher --> UC15
Researcher --> UC16
Researcher --> UC17
Researcher --> UC18
Researcher --> UC19
Researcher --> UC20
Researcher --> UC21
Researcher --> UC22
Researcher --> UC23
Researcher --> UC24
Researcher --> UC25
Researcher --> UC26

' Include relationships
UC1 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC8 ..> UC6 : <<include>>
UC8 ..> UC9 : <<include>>
UC15 ..> UC14 : <<include>>
UC15 ..> UC16 : <<include>>

' Extend relationships
UC3 ..> UC1 : <<extend>>
UC5 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>
UC7 ..> UC6 : <<extend>>
UC11 ..> UC10 : <<extend>>
UC18 ..> UC6 : <<extend>>
UC19 ..> UC6 : <<extend>>

